<item>
            <title>[LU-16233] SUSE 15 SP3 LTSS kernel version 5.3.18-150300.59.93 and later break lustre build tests</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16233</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SUSE 15 SP3 LTSS kernel version 5.3.18-150300.59.93 and later break lustre build tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lustre build tests expect conftest.i to be generated.&lt;br/&gt;
The LTSS kernel uses &apos;always&apos; instead of &apos;always-y&apos; ... so add always as well.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
